arStrings.szText:
(PH) {c_label}{u}Ultimate Jaguar{/u}{/c} 
{icon:bullet,1.2} The Jaguar manifests and bounds around the battlefield for {c_number}{SF_2}{/c} seconds, causing {c_number}6{/c} massive novae that each deal {c_number}{payload:PANTHER_NOVA_DAMAGE}{/c} Fire damage.

{c_important}The Hunter{/c} overfills your {c_important}{u}Ferocity{/u}{/c} by {c_number}{SF_13}{/c} stacks and causes you to deal {c_number}[{SF_14}*100|%x|]{/c} increased damage to {c_important}{u}Injured{/u}{/c} enemies for {c_number}{SF_15}{/c} seconds.
Killing an enemy while {c_important}The Hunter{/c} is present has a {c_number}[{SF_16}*100|%|]{/c} chance to instantly reset its Cooldown. This chance is halved after each consecutive reset.
